allWatches.description: For your consideration is this Vacheron Constantin Fiftysix,a watch with a retro yet highly modern style that makes for a perfect everyday timepiece.
Features include a deep blue dial with sunburst finish, luminous hour/minute hands, running centre seconds, quick-set date and sapphire display case back
The stainless steel bracelet features a double folding clasp with two button safety release system.
Powering the watch is the VC automatic calibre 1326 beating at 28,800 VPH, with a power reserve of 48 hours and hacking seconds function
